{"tid":657544,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係好嬲！我接左份幫輕度弱智兒童補習，個文盲媽媽竟然咁對我！","createTime":"2018-05-08T08:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T13:29:39.000Z","uid":20032,"like":70,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4da31feef28780954fdfc0e37aa11191561f689b","tid":657544,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:02:36.000Z","msg":"前事唔講太多，我一直有補開個學生<br />\n<br />\n總之果日我見個學生唔係幾開心，問佢咩事，佢話d同學成笑佢蠢蠢頓頓，我聽到都好心痛，就同佢講:真正有大智慧嘅人，未必睇落，做落嘅嘢都係好聰明。<br />\n<br />\n我就拎我珍藏嘅書法家畫嘅鎖鑰扣，上面寫著我人生嘅宗旨-大智若愚<br />\n<br />\n我就話:不如你今晚查查個成語點解，下次再解釋下俾我聽啦好無😊<br />\n<br />\n點知當晚家長就打電話嚟:仆街！我已經用&rdquo;谷哥&rdquo;查左讀出嚟啦！鬧我個仔 如弱智大！？陷家產啦你！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n説罷，block埋我電話，仇都無得報"},{"pid":"1d4b95b913936f4a984ea902c0b0a1de2eac2ad2","tid":657544,"uid":65743,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/160356_15807d2be85f37eb47e99b808055fecb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2F160356_15807d2be85f37eb47e99b808055fecb.gif&h=71a2cdea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59b4882cbb7bba41d30ecdb86eb5dc90310e2c15","tid":657544,"uid":78620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:04:12.000Z","msg":"read."},{"pid":"c23a08312f86c9477544990c61e072b171f8cc1f","tid":657544,"uid":6644,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:05:29.000Z","msg":"1.5/10<br />\n<br />\n欠佳"},{"pid":"fe991ef70351c8cb5349f6bd544f2b1c451aa293","tid":657544,"uid":20032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d4b95b913936f4a984ea902c0b0a1de2eac2ad2","tid":657544,"uid":65743,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T08:03:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/08/160356_15807d2be85f37eb47e99b808055fecb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F0